articles.author: Christopher Lamb, Helen Regan, Kathleen Magramo
articles.title: Pope Francis gets rockstar welcome in the world’s most Catholic nation outside of Vatican City - CNN
articles.description: Pope Francis received a rapturous welcome from the tiny Southeast Asian nation of East Timor, one of the world’s most Catholic countries, where more than half the population is expected to turn out for an open-air mass on Tuesday.
